Package producereportscontrollers

package producereportscontrollers
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AreaManager
    This Class is a helper class for AreaManger Controller and the methods that uses it this class is used to set/save information and show/get it
    ProduceCustomersController
    This class is a Produce Customers Report Controller for ProduceCustomersPage.fxml the function of this class is to display information generated by the system of that information are two tables that show information about the customers, the amount of orders and money spent they have.
    ProduceOrdersController
    This class is a Produce Orders Report Controller for ProduceOrdersPage.fxml the function of this class is to display information generated by the system of that information are two tables that show information about the orders, the amount of sales done for each product and profit gained on them, in addition to showing another table that displays each product with the category it is assigned to after reviewing the system-generated reports, the area manager is required to insert information to produce their own report for it to be submitted to the management to see This class also uses other classes to help manage the properties one of the classes is TableRow - which helps us add rows to our table of information with products sold in orders
    ProduceStockController
    This class is a Produce Stock Report Controller for ProduceStockPage.fxml the function of this class is to display information generated by the system of that information are two tables that show information about the stock, the amount of sales done for each category stock percentage daily throughout the month, after reviewing the system-generated reports, the area manager is required to insert information to produce their own report for it to be submitted to the management to see This class also uses other classes to help manage the properties one of the classes is TableRow - which helps us add rows to our table of information with products sold in orders
